
                          Neon M1 Installation
                          ====================

NOTE: this is PRE-ALPHA code. Don't use it on real data, except for
Neon itself.
                        
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Neon uses a custom 'build' script:

	$ cd neon
    $ ./build all
    $ ./build install

PREREQUISITES:

Email me@ariston.dev if you have any problems.
